{
"#name"
:
{
"skill"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"Skill 管理"
,
"en"
:
"Skill Management"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
null
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Manage Agent Skills to enhance LLM task execution.\n\nSkills are reusable capabilities that extend LLM abilities for specific tasks.\nThis module allows you to browse, add, remove, and manage skills for various AI agents.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"管理 Agent Skills，增强 LLM 任务执行能力。\n\nSkills 是可复用的能力扩展，用于增强 LLM 在特定任务上的表现。\n本模块支持浏览、添加、移除和管理多种 AI agent 的 skills。\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Quick start:\n1. Run 'x skill ll' to see all available skills\n2. Run 'x skill ls' to see activated skills in current project\n3. Run 'x skill suggest' to get AI-recommended skills for your project\n"
,
"cn"
:
"快速开始：\n1. 运行 'x skill ll' 查看所有可用 skills\n2. 运行 'x skill ls' 查看当前项目已激活的 skills\n3. 运行 'x skill suggest' 获取 AI 推荐的 skills\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill ll"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有可用 skills"
,
"en"
:
"Example: list all available skills"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出当前项目已激活的 skills"
,
"en"
:
"Example: list activated skills in current project"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill suggest --auto"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 自动应用 AI 推荐的 skills"
,
"en"
:
"Example: auto-apply AI-recommended skills"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill add anthropics/pptx"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 添加 pptx skill"
,
"en"
:
"Example: add pptx skill"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill add anthropics/pptx --agent claude"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 仅为 claude-code agent 添加 pptx skill"
,
"en"
:
"Example: add pptx skill for claude-code agent only"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill add https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-skills --skill gemini-api-dev --skill gemini-interactions-api"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 从 GitHub 仓库添加多个 skills"
,
"en"
:
"Example: add multiple skills from GitHub repo"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x skill rm --skill-dir .claude/skills anthropics/skill-creator"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 从当前项目移除 skill-creator skill"
,
"en"
:
"Example: remove skill-creator skill from current project"
}
]
,
"ll"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有可用 skills（从远程仓库）"
,
"en"
:
"List all available skills from remote repository"
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 CSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in CSV format"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
}
}
,
